race.comment: HELLO EASY (2) comes into this as a quickest on the card winner last time at this track, scoring by 1.3 lengths (19.24). Expected to be in this for a long way. ROB YOU BLIND (8) ran good time (19.31) winning a Grade 4/5 three back at this track but missed the frame latest finishing fifth at this track. Rates a winning chance on best. THAT'S OUR GIRL (4) has a strong winning strike-rate this journey here having won six of seven starts. In the money last time at Nowra (20.98) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 6 length third. Can hit the frame with the right run. WOOLGOOLGA LASS (7) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish in impressive time.
